    <body>
        <div class="main-container">
            <div class="top-bar">
                <div style="margin: auto;">
                    <img class="pepega-logo" src="assets/pepega.png"/>
                </div>
                <div class="socials fun-page">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="container-header">You can find me here:</div>
                        <div class="img-text-link">
                            <a href="https://github.com/k-Knight">
                                <img src="assets/github-logo.png"/>
                                My GitHub
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://gist.github.com/k-Knight" style="margin-left: calc(var(--my_unit) * 3);">
                                <img src="assets/github-logo.png"/>
                                My Gist
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="img-text-link">
                            <a href="https://discordapp.com/users/228184023992631296">
                                <img src="assets/discord-logo.png"/>
                                Me on Discord
                            </a>
                            <div style="margin-left: var(--my_unit); color: #bbb;">k_knight</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="container-header">Website stats</div>
                        <pre class="container-misc site-stats">Unread messages:          1
Serving files:           14
File downloads:         564
</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="flex-container">
                    <div class="container site-fun" style="flex-basis: 10%;">
                        <div class="container-header">File Directory</div>
                        <div class="container-misc">Download files from the website or upload them to it.</div>
                        <div class="container-spacer"></div>
                        <button style = "display: block;" class="pushable">
                            <a href="https://pepega.online/files">
                                <span class="front">Go see files</span>
                            </a>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container site-fun" style="flex-basis: 20%;">
                        <div class="container-header">Minecraft</div>
                        <div class="container-misc">
                            You want to play on my server? Contact me and ask me about it.<br/>
                            I might add you to a whitelist or I might not.<br/><br/>
                            The server is hosted at address <a href="https://pepega.online">pepega.online</a><br/>
                            The modpack currently used for the server:
                            <a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/mrm-experience">
                                MRM Experience
                            </a><br/><br/>
                            If you want to see the map of the server, then follow the link below.
                        </div>
                        <div class="container-spacer"></div>
                        <button style = "display: block;" class="pushable">
                            <a href="https://pepega.online/mc-map">
                                <span class="front">See world map</span>
                            </a>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container site-fun" style="flex-basis: 20%;">
                        <div class="container-header">Magicka 2 Mods</div>
                        <div class="container-misc">
                            Are you bored of same old bugged Magicka 2?<br/>
                            Then try my Magicka 2 mods!<br/><br/>
                            If you want to download them right now, then just <a href="https://pepega.online/download?file=m2_mod_installer.exe">click here</a>.<br/><br/>
                            The tooling and utilities of the mods (including the installer) are open source, you can review the code your self on my <a href="https://github.com/k-Knight/m2-kmf">Github repo</a>.<br/><br/>
                            However, the mods and the loader themselves are not open-source to prevent low-effort copying.
                        </div>
                        <div class="container-header"><br/>I get virus warnings!</div>
                        <div class="container-misc">
                            Please visit this project's <a href="https://github.com/k-Knight/m2-kmf?tab=readme-ov-file#i-get-virus-warnings">Github page</a> to see why that happens and why it is a false positive.
                        </div>
                        <div class="container-header"><br/>I want Tier 2 Access!</div>
                        <div class="container-misc">
                            Please download <a href="https://pepega.online/download?file=m2_tier2_enc.luac">m2_tier2_enc.luac</a> script and install it into &lt;magicka 2 root direcotry&gt;/engine/autoexec/ directory.</br></br>
                            You will need to qualify for access to the Tier 2 functionality by completing in-game challanges.</br></br>
                            Contact me somehow for futher information.
                        </div>
                        <div class="container-spacer"></div>
                        <button style = "display: block;" class="pushable">
                            <a href="https://pepega.online/download?file=m2_mod_installer.exe">
                                <span class="front">Download</span>
                            </a>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container site-fun" style="flex-basis: 20%;">
                        <div class="container-header">You wanna tell me something?</div>
                        <div class="container-misc">
                            You can contact me using the links to socials provided above.<br/>
                            You can also send me a message using website functionality.<br/><br/>
                            Bug reports for the website also go here, I guess.
                        </div>
                        <div class="container-spacer"></div>
                        <button style = "display: block;" class="pushable">
                            <a href="https://pepega.online/message">
                                <span class="front">Leave a message</span>
                            </a>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
